Remixing is one of the most impressive arts of producing. A remix can create an entirely different vibe, and turn a good club tune into a worldwide hit. The remixes on 'Biggest Trance Remixes' Vol.1 are a selection of the biggest, hottest and most legendary remixes with the trance genre. Tunes by Signum, Three Drives, Max Graham, RAM, Dash Berlin, Pulser, Chakra and more, remixed by Armin van Buuren, Aly & Fila, Agnelli & Nelson, W&W, Gareth Emery and more. Absolute must-haves!
